{
  "stem": "1491.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He couldn't walk straight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And next day that lagerfuhrer disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know how he got rid of him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the way I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What do you think happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Either the partisan-- because people were in touch with the underground, Czechoslovakian underground, either they got rid of him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think he got rid of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How and what, I--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got him drunk and he walked him through that place where we work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he disappeared and we were saved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, purposely did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How and what, I heard rumors, but they were rumors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody said he put him on a carriage and the partisans got rid of him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other people said that gave him a strong letter, he has to go to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he disappeared, and we'd been saved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was so-- he couldn't walk straight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the war ended, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we didn't know the war ended even.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Through the gates from the camp, I saw Germans running away with white flags.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We knew we going to be free.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Schindler disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we were left like alone without any power, without anybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think I would say two days after the war ended, a Russian soldier came in on a horse [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and told us, you are liberated.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We kissed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We kissed him that you can't imagine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they were such animals, the Russians, when they walked in, so we didn't know which we were better off.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
